Given the watch is in mode "on"
Then the first button must be called "mode"

When the watch enters mode "on"
Then the "display" must show "hello"


Given the watch is in mode "off"
Then the first button must be called "mode"

When the watch enters mode "off"
Then the "display" must show ""

Given the watch is in mode "off"
When the first button is pressed
Then the watch must be in mode "on"